edu.rit.util

Class PriorityQueue<T extends PriorityQueue.Item>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.rit.util.PriorityQueue<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Item data type.

    public class PriorityQueue<T extends PriorityQueue.Item>
extends java.lang.Object
    Class PriorityQueue provides a priority queue. The items in the queue are instances of a subclass of class PriorityQueue.Item. Items are removed from the queue in priority order, as determined by the item's comesBefore() method.
